objects.description: The [Exaramel for Windows](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0343) dropper creates and starts a Windows service named wsmprovav with the description “Windows Check AV” in an apparent attempt to masquerade as a legitimate service.(Citation: ESET TeleBots Oct 2018)
